headline: Why Tyler Technologies Stock Slipped on Monday
summary: Tyler Technologies (NYSE: TYL) was given the cold shoulder by analysts on the first trading day of the week.  Analysts often make tweaks to their stock evaluations after earnings; this one closely follows Tyler's latest earnings release.
